76561198123750907,Recommended,229520,11307709,"Posted: 18 July, 2014",all,EyesHerEndHer,"Dungeon Hearts is a match 3 puzzle game.  Dungeons hearts adds some enjoyable elements to make this millionth iteration of match 3 games a bit more fun.  There are blocks that are sent by the enemy to slow you down.  Your goal is to crush the enemy while stopping his attacks.  As you progress through the game you get certain skills that fall outside simple block movements that can get you out of a pickle.  You also gain experience which gives your characters different abilities.  This gives the player a chance to feel like they can actually beat the game even if their skills aren't up to snuff to make it to the last boss.  There is an incentive to keep playing and boost your skills so that those final levels don't seem to tough.  If you are into puzzle games and don't mind staring at moving blocks all day, you will probably enjoy this game.  If you are sick of the million different iterations of puzzle games, I would probably pick up something else.Follow us onhttps://www.google.com/+Brick-mediato see more reviews, walkthroughs etc."
